query.sfwSql:
INSERT INTO SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_HISTORY ( PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID, START_DATE, END_DATE, PROVIDER_ORG_ID, PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_ID, PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE, STATUS_ID, STATUS_VALUE, FROM_PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID, TO_PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID, SUPPRESS_WARNINGS_FLAG, SUPPRESS_WARNINGS_BY, SUPPRESS_WARNINGS_DATE, DC_ELIGIBILITY_DATE, MUTUAL_FUND_WINDOW_FLAG, CAPITAL_GAIN, RHIC_BENFIT_AMOUNT, VESTING_LETTER_SENT_FLAG, CREATED_BY, CREATED_DATE, MODIFIED_BY, MODIFIED_DATE, UPDATE_SEQ ) SELECT A.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID, A.START_DATE, A.END_DATE, A.PROVIDER_ORG_ID, A.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_ID, A.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE, A.STATUS_ID, A.STATUS_VALUE, A.FROM_PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID, A.TO_PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID, A.SUPPRESS_WARNINGS_FLAG, A.SUPPRESS_WARNINGS_BY, A.SUPPRESS_WARNINGS_DATE, C.DC_ELIGIBILITY_DATE, C.MUTUAL_FUND_WINDOW_FLAG, C.CAPITAL_GAIN, C.RHIC_BENFIT_AMOUNT, C.VESTING_LETTER_SENT_FLAG, 'PERSLink Batch'+' '+ convert(nvarchar,@batchscheduleid) as CREATED_BY ,getdate() as CREATED_DATE, 'PERSLink Batch'+' '+ convert(nvarchar,@batchscheduleid) as MODIFIED_BY ,getdate() as MODIFIED_DATE,0 UPDATE_SEQ FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT A INNER JOIN( SELECT PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID,PLAN_PARTIPATION_STATUS,HISTORY_CHANGE_DATE FROM( SELECT PA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID,pa.BENEFIT_BEGIN_DATE, BA.MEMBER_PERSON_ID,BA.PLAN_ID,BAPA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID, PA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_ID,PA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE, case when PA.BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE in ('RGRD','AURD') then 'WTN1' when PA.BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE = 'DBCT' then 'TRDC' when PA.BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE = 'SPEL' then 'TRDC' when PA.BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE = 'DTCT' then 'TICR' END AS PLAN_PARTIPATION_STATUS,@PAYMENTDATE AS HISTORY_CHANGE_DATE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT PA (NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS PAS(NOLOCK) ON PAS.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER PHH ON PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID=PA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV ON PAS.STATUS_ID= CV.CODE_ID AND PAS.STATUS_VALUE = CV.CODE_VALUE INNER JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION BA ON PA.Application_id = ba.benefit_application_id INNER JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION_PERSON_ACCOUNT BAPA ON BA.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID=BAPA.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID and isnull(IS_APPLICATION_PERSON_ACCOUNT_FLAG,'N') = 'Y' WHERE (CV.DATA2 = 'APRD' ) AND PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS_ID = (SELECT TOP 1 PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS_ID FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS PAS1 (nolock) WHERE PAS1.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID AND PAS1.STATUS_EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @PAYMENTDATE ORDER BY PAS1.STATUS_EFFECTIVE_DATE DESC,PAS1.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS_ID DESC ) AND BENEFIT_BEGIN_DATE <= @PAYMENTDATE AND (BENEFIT_END_DATE IS NULL OR BENEFIT_END_DATE > @PAYMENTDATE) AND PA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE = 'RFND' AND ( PA.BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE in ('DBCT','DTCT','SPEL') OR ( PA.BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE in ('RGRD','AURD') AND BA.HARDSHIP_APPROVED_FLAG = 'Y' ) ) AND PHH.PAYMENT_SCHEDULE_ID=@PAYMENTSCHEDULEID )PERSONACCOUNT
UNION ALL
SELECT PERSONACCOUNT.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID,PERSONACCOUNT.PLAN_PARTIPATION_STATUS,PERSONACCOUNT.HISTORY_CHANGE_DATE FROM ( SELECT PA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID,pa.BENEFIT_BEGIN_DATE, BA.MEMBER_PERSON_ID,BA.PLAN_ID,BAPA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID, PA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_ID,PA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE, case when PA.BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE = 'DBDC' then 'TRTF' when PA.BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE = 'DBTT' then 'TRTF' end AS PLAN_PARTIPATION_STATUS,@PAYMENTDATE AS HISTORY_CHANGE_DATE, (isNull(BRC.POST_TAX_EE_CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT,0.00) + isNull(BRC.PRE_TAX_EE_CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT,0.00)+ isNull(BRC.EE_ER_PICKUP_AMOUNT,0.00) + isNull(BRC.RHIC_EE_AMOUNT,0.00)+isNull(BRC.EE_INTEREST_AMOUNT,0.00)+isNull(BRC.VESTED_ER_CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT ,0.00)) AS TOTALAMOUNT FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT PA (NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS PAS(NOLOCK) ON PAS.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER PHH ON PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID=PA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV ON PAS.STATUS_ID= CV.CODE_ID AND PAS.STATUS_VALUE = CV.CODE_VALUE INNER JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION BA ON PA.Application_id = ba.benefit_application_id INNER JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION_PERSON_ACCOUNT BAPA ON BA.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID=BAPA.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID and isnull(IS_APPLICATION_PERSON_ACCOUNT_FLAG,'N') = 'Y' INNER JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_REFUND_CALCULATION BRC ON BRC.BENEFIT_CALCULATION_ID=PA.CALCULATION_ID WHERE (CV.DATA2 = 'APRD' ) AND PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS_ID = (SELECT TOP 1 PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS_ID FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS PAS1 (nolock) WHERE PAS1.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID AND PAS1.STATUS_EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @PAYMENTDATE ORDER BY PAS1.STATUS_EFFECTIVE_DATE DESC,PAS1.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS_ID DESC ) AND BENEFIT_BEGIN_DATE <= @PAYMENTDATE AND (BENEFIT_END_DATE IS NULL OR BENEFIT_END_DATE > @PAYMENTDATE) AND PA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE = 'RFND' AND PA.BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE in ('DBDC','DBTT') AND BA.HARDSHIP_APPROVED_FLAG = 'Y' AND PHH.PAYMENT_SCHEDULE_ID=@PAYMENTSCHEDULEID) PERSONACCOUNT INNER JOIN ( SELECT PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID,sum(isNull(POST_TAX_EE_AMOUNT,0.00) + isNull(PRE_TAX_EE_AMOUNT,0.00) + isNull(EE_RHIC_AMOUNT,0.00) + isNull(EE_ER_PICKUP_AMOUNT,0.00) + isNull(ER_VESTED_AMOUNT,0.00) + isNull(INTEREST_AMOUNT,0.00)) AS CONTRIBAMT FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_CONTRIBUTION GROUP BY PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID )CONTR ON PERSONACCOUNT.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID=CONTR.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID WHERE TOTALAMOUNT= CONTR.CONTRIBAMT )B ON A.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID=B.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT C ON C.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID=B.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID

SELECT * FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_HISTORY WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL1' AND START_DATE <> ISNULL(END_DATE,'99991231') AND PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = @PERSONACCOUNTID AND (@STARTDATE BETWEEN START_DATE AND ISNULL(END_DATE,'99991231') OR @ENDDATE BETWEEN START_DATE AND ISNULL(END_DATE,'99991231') OR START_DATE BETWEEN @STARTDATE AND @ENDDATE OR ISNULL(END_DATE,'99991231') BETWEEN @STARTDATE AND @ENDDATE) ORDER BY PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_HISTORY_ID DESC
UPDATE SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_HISTORY SET IS_ENROLLMENT_REPORT_GENERATED = 'N' WHERE PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_HISTORY_ID = @HISTORY_ID

UPDATE SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_HISTORY SET IS_ENROLLMENT_REPORT_GENERATED = 'Y' WHERE PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_HISTORY_ID IN ( SELECT TOP 1 PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_HISTORY_ID FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_HISTORY WHERE PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = @PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID AND PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL1' ORDER BY START_DATE DESC )
